{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-post-js","path":"/project/hopefuls","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Presidential Hopefuls","updated":"November 25, 2019","permalink":"/project/hopefuls","timeframe":"Nov. 2019","tools":"Figma, HTML/CSS, Javascript, Adobe Photoshop","link":"https://www.rence.la/","coverimage":{"absolutePath":"D:/Document/Github/formula-update/src/images/projectimages/hopefulsheader.jpg"}},"id":"09d32ead-c167-5a93-a6a5-f9022d0ef7ec","html":"<div class=\"csblock\" id=\"context\"> \n<span class=\"csblockheading\">\n    Context\n</span>\n    As a critical election year neared, the <a href=\"https://thepolitic.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Yale Politic</a> wanted to chronicle their series of interviews over the past decade to offer more insight into the presidential candidates. The Tech Team was tasked with the creation of a minisite that would present the interviews in a meaningful and accessible way.\n</div>\n<div class=\"csblock\" id=\"team\"> \n<span class=\"csblockheading\">\n    Team\n</span>\n    Under the leadership of the <a href=\"https://chiaski.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">team lead</a>, we aimed to expand readership for the magazine and build a template for future feature projects. Personally, I was responsible for the landing page design, as well as content and asset generation.\n</div>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 30.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Politic Header' title='Politic Header' src='/static/e34025ff364d2bd5423fdc084089c754/644c5/hopefulsheader.jpg' srcset='/static/e34025ff364d2bd5423fdc084089c754/066f9/hopefulsheader.jpg 400w,\n/static/e34025ff364d2bd5423fdc084089c754/4b190/hopefulsheader.jpg 800w,\n/static/e34025ff364d2bd5423fdc084089c754/644c5/hopefulsheader.jpg 1440w' sizes='(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy'>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"csblock\" id=\"concept\">  \n<span class=\"csblockheading\">\n    Concept\n</span>\n    According to initial sketches, the landing page would showcase several prominent interviewees, with their photos and names, as well as an impactful presentation, which differed from The Politic’s usual, more muted style.\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"/projectimages/.jpg\" alt=\"Politic Sketches\"></p>\n<div class=\"csblock\" id=\"prototype\"> \n<span class=\"csblockheading\">\n    Prototype\n</span>\n    The landing page was prototyped in Figma, originally featuring a large, bold font with black and white motif to capitalize on the preexisting design language of the magazine. In a similar vein, the candidate photos are prescribed a black and white treatment. To equalize and humanize the candidates, I conceived of the technique of blurring and adding grains to the portraits through Photoshop.\n</div>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1152px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 60.74999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Politic Prototype' title='Politic Prototype' src='/static/893752ea7eee120f3ed5ebec7cef96c7/5ef17/hopefulsfigma.jpg' srcset='/static/893752ea7eee120f3ed5ebec7cef96c7/066f9/hopefulsfigma.jpg 400w,\n/static/893752ea7eee120f3ed5ebec7cef96c7/4b190/hopefulsfigma.jpg 800w,\n/static/893752ea7eee120f3ed5ebec7cef96c7/5ef17/hopefulsfigma.jpg 1152w' sizes='(max-width: 1152px) 100vw, 1152px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy'>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"csblock\" id=\"implementation\"> \n<span class=\"csblockheading\">\n    Implementation\n</span>\n    With the goal of encouraging readers to go through all the content, we implemented a system of horizontal slider and vertical scrolling, such that all interviews with minimum clicks and scrolls. For typography, Canela was used for headings as it brings a kind of elegance different from the magazine’s usual Georgia, and Sailek was chosen for the body.\n</div>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 30.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Politic Final 1' title='Politic Final 1' src='/static/75ec46d7f8adc59ebef20f149b4024ae/644c5/hopefulstype.jpg' srcset='/static/75ec46d7f8adc59ebef20f149b4024ae/066f9/hopefulstype.jpg 400w,\n/static/75ec46d7f8adc59ebef20f149b4024ae/4b190/hopefulstype.jpg 800w,\n/static/75ec46d7f8adc59ebef20f149b4024ae/644c5/hopefulstype.jpg 1440w' sizes='(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy'>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"csblock\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"> \n    The site was developed with a mobile-first mindset to account for The Politic’s largely mobile readership. On mobile devices, clicking the fixed header brings up a list of all the candidates, allowing quick access without excessive scrolling. \n</div>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 42.75000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Politic Final 2' title='Politic Final 2' src='/static/b3e593195c94cb37c7c22830ce829bc2/07a9c/hopefulsmobile.png' srcset='/static/b3e593195c94cb37c7c22830ce829bc2/e17e5/hopefulsmobile.png 400w,\n/static/b3e593195c94cb37c7c22830ce829bc2/5a190/hopefulsmobile.png 800w,\n/static/b3e593195c94cb37c7c22830ce829bc2/07a9c/hopefulsmobile.png 1440w' sizes='(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy'>\n    </span>\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 16.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Politic Final 2' title='Politic Final 2' src='/static/258e42dc78c440920f9527d223af0102/644c5/hopefulsbanner.jpg' srcset='/static/258e42dc78c440920f9527d223af0102/066f9/hopefulsbanner.jpg 400w,\n/static/258e42dc78c440920f9527d223af0102/4b190/hopefulsbanner.jpg 800w,\n/static/258e42dc78c440920f9527d223af0102/644c5/hopefulsbanner.jpg 1440w' sizes='(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy'>\n    </span>\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 48.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Politic Final 3' title='Politic Final 3' src='/static/cfd70f99d3bd8e4f65b5d02fe1838b50/07a9c/hopefulslayout.png' srcset='/static/cfd70f99d3bd8e4f65b5d02fe1838b50/e17e5/hopefulslayout.png 400w,\n/static/cfd70f99d3bd8e4f65b5d02fe1838b50/5a190/hopefulslayout.png 800w,\n/static/cfd70f99d3bd8e4f65b5d02fe1838b50/07a9c/hopefulslayout.png 1440w' sizes='(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy'>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"csblock\" id=\"results\"> \n<span class=\"csblockheading\">\n    Results\n</span>\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 5px;\">\n        <li> <i>Learned the fundamentals of web development.</i> Introduced to prototyping with Figma, version control, and responsive design.\n        <li> <i>Practiced the process of design thinking.</i> From conceptualization to sketches to implementation, the process turned out to be a constant compromise between vision and usability, creativity and human-centered thinking.\n    </ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"Politic Sketches"}},"pageContext":{"next":null,"previous":{"frontmatter":{"permalink":"/project/adobe","title":"Grow Together"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["4257582160","63159454"]}